item.title: All water is lava?

Logs or something? * 6 = Red roofing * 5 = Really dark wood texture * 4 = Elven doors * 3 = Wooden flooring * 2 = Stone walls (i.e. on Varrock banks, etc) * 1 = Water * 0 = Door
